subject: Where's everyone gone?
msgSnippet: I ve finally gotten to the point where I can not only read QuickScript reliably (though slowly), but can write it almost useably fast. Now the party s over and
messageBody:
I've finally gotten to the point where I can not only read
QuickScript reliably (though slowly), but can write it almost useably
fast.
Now the party's over and everyone's gone. The Ikonboard
(Shavian.org?) is almost as quiet. Is this just a bad season?

I was hoping to get some feedback on my font's lettershapes so I
can start the hand-kerning process. Any comments, anyone?
Anyone?
